<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦拉上窗帘，她非常伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在湖里只剩下淤泥和岩石，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有一些在淤泥里努力跳动的鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刚开始，艾伦的父母以为她会哭，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是没有眼泪流出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦把自己关在了房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女巫的咒语起作用了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦忘记了王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她忘记了所有人，包括她的父母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王宫里再也听不到她的笑声了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子还是每天去湖边，去等艾伦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，他终于明白了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾伦再也不会回来了，”王子心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须要知道她现在好不好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子穿上仆人的衣服，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他去了王宫，假装在那里工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一边擦靴子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一边问其他人艾伦的情况。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>结果他们都说：“公主快要死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子的心里一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他必须要去救她！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是要怎么救呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要想一个计划。”王子决定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和王后也不知道该怎么办。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像以前那样，国王又慢慢没有了耐心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把柯普和哈姆请来吧。”王后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许他们可以解释湖水为什么变干，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样我们就能恢复湖水了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>柯普和哈姆仔细观察了湖底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们讨论了变干的河流和喷泉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>讨论了婴儿的眼泪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们还是没有找到问题的原因。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天下午，一个男孩儿来见国王和王后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿着一个金盘子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下！我在湖底的淤泥里发现了这个，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得它上面有关于湖水的线索。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”国王接过盘子，上面写满了文字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一首长诗。”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它讲了一个可以恢复湖水的神奇方法！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么方法？”王后很激动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“湖底有个洞，”国王解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“必须要有一个人爬进洞里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后用自己的身体把洞堵上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像软木塞那样？”王后问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个软木塞……嗯，这个人必须献出自己的生命。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悲伤地看着王后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去哪里找这样一位勇敢的英雄呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>